May be an image of text that says 'Lukemia donations $4,070 raised of $20,000 goal Bob Tocco Longview, CA Hi this is Bob Tocco and this is my grand daughter in the picture, her daddy and my Son Cory was diagnosed this week with Lukemia and I'm putting together a fundraiser to help with medical bills & home bills to keep family stabe while he is hospitalized. ask more'.

node.text: Go fund me link in bio‼️ Not the news I wanted to hear but it is time to spread the word and support a friend from the Moto family @ctocco188 . Cory is a hard-working family man who has always been a man of his word. I have never seen anyone work as hard as this guy. He has built many tracks for us in moto and offroad . Corey and his wife just had a daughter. Let’s support him through his fight with leukemia. Spread the word.  Life is precious and very fragile let’s make sure we support our fellow people. Thank You !  #MotoFamily A friend in need is a friend indeed!
